{"tid":1978250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮記者會有個上海衛視記者唔認自己係黨媒 遭特朗普革扯！！！","createTime":"2020-04-18T14:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T02:51:42.000Z","uid":28114,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba1fc4e6714bfe646a134d20bae01f023ab1b4e5","tid":1978250,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/donald-trump-cut-off-ccp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fdonald-trump-cut-off-ccp.jpg&h=988816b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為中國人不認中國人，硬係要稱為香港人，搞港獨搞分裂的記者，我們之前都見過。最近一名為黨媒上海衛視工作的台灣人張經義，在白宮記者會時被美國總統特朗普問來自哪裏，他不認自己為中國黨媒工作，更沒有配合中國黨媒的方向，否認來自中國，自稱來自台灣，大肆搞台獨。<br />\n<br />\n台灣人早就此事不停討論，事件終於傳回美國。美國人Charlie Kirk再次向外發表文章，問道為什麼中國黨媒經常入侵白宮，影片就是張經義提問的片段。美國總統特朗普亦首次RT並公開狂罵，寫「Cut him off now!」，要求踢張經義離開。有人對此讚好，既然是中共口舌就不是真記者，但亦有左膠認為，這樣與中共無分別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1251354896651223041?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1251354896651223041%3Fs%3D21&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6ca132cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1251354896651223041%3Fs%3D21&h=9b68d3ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1251354896651223041?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/donald-trump-kick-off-the-taiwan-reporter-who-works-for-ccp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fdonald-trump-kick-off-the-taiwan-reporter-who-works-for-ccp%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=98a13f6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/donald-trump-kick-off-the-taiwan-reporter-who-works-for-ccp/</a>"},{"pid":"cb0bc17b3102dfe8cf4916c24e06abee31dad25c","tid":1978250,"ui